{"tid":378387,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【STEM】巴士到站無位坐？　中學生研「指南巴」系統顯示即時座位數量","createTime":"2017-08-28T12:41:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T12:50:30.000Z","uid":36238,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c2254541d6346599425e6cc21b25c6779d9575ad","tid":378387,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T12:41:19.000Z","msg":"苦等許久，巴士只有企位，怎樣可以才獲得更多即時資訊？這班中學生可能幫到你。第50屆聯校科學展覽具23個創意方案，如有庇理羅士女子中學的「燈」車易、聖保祿中學的「指路明燈」、慈幼英文學校的「指南巴」（Infomnibus）等，他們為了解決市民在生活上遇到的困難以提出不同的改善方案，究竟他們是如何把天馬行空的想像，化為可行的方案？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/204012_ce2eff70edc0b82125a7d328607701f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F204012_ce2eff70edc0b82125a7d328607701f7.jpg&h=8c2a2988&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>「指南巴」：RFID系統偵測座位情況<br />\n</strong><br />\n提出「指南巴」方案是慈幼英文學校的中五學生，他們認為除了港鐵，巴士便是另一個最主要的交通工具，可是有時會出現，等了許久已滿坐的情況，他們希望可以提供更多資訊，讓市民考慮應否乘坐即將到站的巴士。他們的構思是在一、二月開始成形，就是在巴士及巴士站上安裝無線射頻識別系統（RFID），他們說：「巴士就類似八達通，巴士站就像八達通機，當巴士經過巴士站，便會傳送資訊，如何時離開、有多少坐位。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/204028_f8de0995198d98e04d9ab23527b52cda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F204028_f8de0995198d98e04d9ab23527b52cda.jpg&h=55d05f46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>如何知道座位數量？<br />\n</strong><br />\n他們會在每個座位設置紅外傳感器（Infrared Sensor），這樣便可準確地知道有多少座位是使用中。另外，他們亦會設一個壓力傳感器（Pressure Sensor）在巴士的下層，以巴士的重量作一個乘客密度的預算，有多少乘客正在站立，再以三個燈號顯示巴士的擁擠情況，如綠燈便是沒有人或是少人站立、橙色為一般、紅色就是爆滿。<br />\n<br />\n雖然他們在第50屆聯校科學展覽計劃書設計比賽中並未獲得獎項，但是他們在聯校科展中設計了一個街道模型及座椅感應器，清楚地解釋「指南巴」是如何運作，而聯校科展是開放大眾參觀及可可親自投票選出心水隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/790971/xlarge/706849254d495c9a2765456e2238b0b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F790971%2Fxlarge%2F706849254d495c9a2765456e2238b0b2.jpg&h=38e34058&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3bc2de83e60426091f86d8c4939cedb695caad23","tid":378387,"uid":36238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T12:41:55.000Z","msg":"<strong>「燈車易」奪冠：改善港鐵「沙甸魚」現象<br />\n</strong><br />\n今屆科學計劃書設計比賽的主題是「社群」，參賽作品或調查須從社群的安全性和舒適性兩方面著手，找出需改進或創造的地方。而今次比賽冠軍是庇理羅士女子中學，他們研發出「燈車易」，意念是透過紅外線探測系統，計算地鐵車廂的乘客密度，再轉發出紅、綠、黃色三種信號燈。她們暫時的設定是把燈號設置於每月台上，「紅」色為最擠迫、「黃」色為不擠迫；再進一步的方案就是把資訊即時傳送至手機應用程式。她們希望，市民可方透過「燈車易」掌握人流情況，從而選擇登上較不擁迫的車廂，讓市民乘搭時更安全舒適。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/204146_6081a5996c225d16013892da445fead9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F204146_6081a5996c225d16013892da445fead9.jpg&h=1f06b673&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b22341e97cdb5335118d1ae8aa9b8e22f3e6e9e","tid":378387,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T12:42:15.000Z","msg":"<strong>「灰飛煙滅」：防止垃圾桶上煙灰缸的黑煙撒播<br />\n</strong><br />\n季軍作品有兩個，其中一個是何文田官立中學，四人團隊設計出一個名為「灰飛煙滅」的特製煙灰缸。他們的構思源自有天在街上走走，看到垃圾桶上還未熄滅的香煙而來。桶上煙灰缸充斥煙臭味，他們希望在不影響吸煙者及非吸煙者的情況下，改善煙臭的問題，因此他們利用超聲波傳感器，以控制煙灰缸蓋的開關，除可防止黑煙散播外，亦可減少煙頭復燃的機會。特製煙灰缸更內含化學物料把煙霧過濾，去除煙霧中的乙醛，從而減少臭味。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/204214_a6508c7fd47e3a1a6c7cae93c4128a5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F204214_a6508c7fd47e3a1a6c7cae93c4128a5d.jpg&h=a542b911&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d3b56c6f0c833b9ac105b38fb4761cba45c3a85","tid":378387,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T12:42:40.000Z","msg":"<strong>「指路明燈」：完善現有交通系統<br />\n</strong><br />\n另一季軍作品為聖保祿中學的「指路明燈」，她們希望完善現有交通系統，提升市民對路面情況的警覺性外，亦希望減少交通意外的發生，因此她們利用三種感應器探測馬路上駛過的車輛，另設蜂鳴器並發出燈光提醒途人有車輛經過；另亦設倒數計時器，提醒司機及路人還有幾多時間才轉另一個燈號。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/204239_e7bc314e07d1b339276bf36bf19657af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F204239_e7bc314e07d1b339276bf36bf19657af.jpg&h=19eb7b78&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"528e550485405a9b57860472ad219380ae92884b","tid":378387,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T12:43:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%A6%AA%E5%AD%90/114435/%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E5%88%B0%E7%AB%99%E7%84%A1%E4%BD%8D%E5%9D%90-%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%A0%94-%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%E5%B7%B4-%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%BA%A7%E4%BD%8D%E6%95%B8%E9%87%8F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%2F114435%2F%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%2588%25B0%25E7%25AB%2599%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BD%258D%25E5%259D%2590-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%25A0%2594-%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%258D%2597%25E5%25B7%25B4-%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E9%25A1%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25BA%25A7%25E4%25BD%258D%25E6%2595%25B8%25E9%2587%258F&d=mD2hx2PZ2ZJI7FJ23SHwShFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=b55c3ff7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%A6%AA%E5%AD%90/114435/%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E5%88%B0%E7%AB%99%E7%84%A1%E4%BD%8D%E5%9D%90-%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%A0%94-%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%E5%B7%B4-%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%BA%A7%E4%BD%8D%E6%95%B8%E9%87%8F</a>"},{"pid":"b05e686892485838181b59ec952646047b449fbf","tid":378387,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T12:44:07.000Z","msg":"計劃書設計比賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eceebfdccace05b296d7ecc344f0c1aa89e175ee","tid":378387,"uid":6959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T12:45:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f96cebcafab5eacce9b3245ff9a2466f0e573fc","tid":378387,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T12:45:09.000Z","msg":"pressure sensor?點計幾多人企幾多人坐呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d36451b1a5f6ee594e6e9d9268a4d5c2bb4553cf","tid":378387,"uid":16320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T12:49:36.000Z","msg":"放個手袋o係位做數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"542343306ed70bcbdb72c16a2ea51adbc553f557","tid":378387,"uid":72280,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T12:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://thesmartlocal.com/images/easyblog_articles/2955/image18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthesmartlocal.com%2Fimages%2Feasyblog_articles%2F2955%2Fimage18.jpg&h=b818723b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.straitstimes.com/sites/default/files/styles/xxx_large/public/articles/2016/03/11/37708433.1_37719242_-_11_03_2016_-_pixbus.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.straitstimes.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fxxx_large%2Fpublic%2Farticles%2F2016%2F03%2F11%2F37708433.1_37719242_-_11_03_2016_-_pixbus.jpg&h=923047d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新加坡用左五年"}]}